tItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pcd1665702916314.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pcd1665702916314.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pcd1665702916314.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pcd1665702916314\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Describes the requested ordering of selected records.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__section_ep5_4f3_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1085023e50\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129929e1_d129930e1_d129931e1\">An array of <code class=\"ph codeph\">uordlst</code> structures\n        (informally called the order-by list), is used to describe the requested ordering of\n        selected records. Uniface supports multifield ordering—if two records are equal with respect\n        to the first entry in the order-by list, they are ordered according to the second entry and\n        so on. If two records are identical in all fields in the order-by list, their order is\n        undefined.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129932e1_d129933e1_d129934e1\">If the DBMS is not capable of selecting records in the\n        requested order, Uniface can handle the sorting.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129935e1_d129936e1_d129937e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uordlst</code> structure is also used to\n        specify the computation to be performed in the Select mode 4 request. For more information,\n        see the \"Database Connector Requests topic\".</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129938e1_d129939e1_d129940e1\">The connector can access the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uordlst</code>\n        structure by using the address of the first element provided in the current\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl</code> structure. The order-by list is available in:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129941e1_d129942e1_d129943e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ControlBlock</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-&gt;uolist[0]...</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129944e1_d129945e1_d129946e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ControlBlock</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-&gt;uolist[(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ControlBlock</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-&gt;uonum -1)]</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__p_d129947e1_d129948e1_d129949e1\">where <var class=\"keyword varname\">ControlBlock</var> contains the\n        address of the current <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl</code> structure.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__section_odp_j1s_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1085023e114\">Members</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">uordlst Members</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__1\">Member </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">short ufnr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__2\">Field number (an index into the field list). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">short uorder</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pcd1665702916314__table_d15461e1_d15462e1_d15463e1__entry__2\">Ordering code; one of: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__ul_sg2_l1s_bcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__li_d46703e1_d46704e1_d46705e1\">0—Ascending order. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pcd1665702916314__li_d46706e1_d46707e1_d46708e1\">1—Descending order. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/job1665702916386.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Connector Requests</a><p>A database connector implements a set of generic Uniface requests for the underlying DBMS. Connector requests are well-defined tasks performed by the DBMS connector when it is called.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530865\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uordlst Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Describes the requested ordering of selected records. Description An array of uordlst structures (informally called the order-by list), is used to describe the requested ordering of selected records. Uniface supports multifield ordering—if two records are equal with respect to the first entry in the order-by list, they are ordered according to the second entry and so on. If two records are identical in all fields in the order-by list, their order is undefined. If the DBMS is not capable of selecting records in the requested order, Uniface can handle the sorting. The uordlst structure is also used to specify the computation to be performed in the Select mode 4 request. For more information, see the \"Database Connector Requests topic\". The connector can access the uordlst structure by using the address of the first element provided in the current uctrl structure. The order-by list is available in: ControlBlock ->uolist[0]... ControlBlock ->uolist[( ControlBlock ->uonum -1)] where ControlBlock contains the address of the current uctrl structure. Members Table 1. uordlst Members Member Description short ufnr Field number (an index into the field list). short uorder Ordering code; one of: 0—Ascending order. 1—Descending order. Related Links Database Connector Requests A database connector implements a set of generic Uniface requests for the underlying DBMS. Connector requests are well-defined tasks performed by the DBMS connector when it is called. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}